OL,3,CMOT testing delay concerns after 16
OL,4,Clifts found to have hairline cracks
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised about
OL,7,Ftesting delays after it's understood
OL,8,F16 MOT lifts were found to have
OL,9,Fhairline cracks.
OL,11,FDUP Fermanagh and South Tyrone MLA and
OL,12,FChair of the Infrastructure committee
OL,13,FDeborah Erskine has highlighted the
OL,14,Fissue after the cracks were found on
OL,15,FMaHa lifts, which were at the centre
OL,16,Fof MOT testing delays in 2019.
