OL,6,F"Overall it cost the Department nearly
OL,7,F#4million in terms of backlogs to the
OL,8,FMOT testing system.
OL,10,F"How have we managed to reach the same
OL,11,Fsituation again? Whilst the number is
OL,12,Fthought to be 14 lifts, with a lift
OL,13,Fsent to Germany for further testing,
OL,14,Fit will undoubtedly cause concern
OL,15,Famongst DVA testing centre employees
OL,16,Fand the general public.
