OL,3,CMOT testing delay concerns after 16
OL,4,Clifts found to have hairline cracks
OL,6,F"Undoubtedly it will cause further
OL,7,Fdelays in our MOT testing. Therefore
OL,8,Fwhilst we await the outcome of testing
OL,9,Fin Germany to the lifts, it is
OL,10,Fimportant that the Minister clearly
OL,11,Foutlines what he and his Department
OL,12,Fare doing to curb the looming crisis.
OL,13,FLessons should have been learnt from
OL,14,F2019 and it is important that we are
OL,15,Fhonest with the public.
