OL,3,CMOT testing delay concerns after 16
OL,4,Clifts found to have hairline cracks
OL,6,F"I was unable to request answers
OL,7,Fdirectly from the Minister today in
OL,8,Fthe Assembly chamber, but I will be
OL,9,Fasking DVA to provide the most up to
OL,10,Fdate information to the Infrastructure
OL,11,FCommittee, and ensure everything is
OL,12,Fbeing done to assure the public and
OL,13,Femployees."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Driver and
OL,16,FVehicle Agency said: "The Driver and
OL,17,FVehicle Agency can confirm that their
OL,18,Fequipment provider has identified
OL,19,Fsmall hairline cracks in the welds of
OL,20,Fthe main scissor bushing of 16 lifts
OL,21,Facross the test centre network.
