OL,3,CMOT testing delay concerns after 16
OL,4,Clifts found to have hairline cracks
OL,6,F"Independent inspectors have reported
OL,7,Ftheir findings on the hairline cracks
OL,8,Fas category C, which is their lowest
OL,9,Fcategory. These hairline cracks are
OL,10,Fnot the same issue as the cracks
OL,11,Fidentified in scissor lifts at the end
OL,12,Fof 2019, early 2020.
OL,14,F"The DVA has robust maintenance
OL,15,Farrangements in place to ensure all
OL,16,Fvehicle testing equipment operates
OL,17,Fsafely and effectively. All lifts
OL,18,Fremain in service and MoT appointments
OL,19,Fhave not been affected.
